    <content>&lt;P&gt;Now I found which device type is logged on, when I go to the Debug Mode -&amp;gt; Data Model -&amp;gt; /Root/$System/DeviceType.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Another option:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;User Menu -&amp;gt; Adaptation Mode -&amp;gt; Implementation -&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp; Rules and Validation -&amp;gt; Rule: DEVICETYPE()=="DESKTOP"&lt;/P&gt;</content>
